  title: Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind
  genre: Drama 2
  position: 34
  description: Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure
    to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches
    his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be
    too late to correct his mistake.
